OL,5,G1250 Broken Arrow
OL,6,     F(1950) Western starring James
OL,7,     FStewart. A gold prospector, tired
OL,8,     Fof reprisal killings between
OL,9,     Fwhites and Native Americans,
OL,10,     Foffers a truce to the Apaches'
OL,11,     Fleader. But tensions resurface.
OL,12,G1440 Fixed Bayonets!
OL,13,     F(1951) Korean War drama about the
OL,14,     Fstress of battle. Officers drop
OL,15,     Fone by one as a US platoon fights
OL,16,     Fa rearguard action, leaving one
OL,17,     Funwilling man (Richard Basehart)
OL,18,     Fto take their place.
